Peppermint fluff sounds like something that flows in rivers of Christmas carol lands, but it‚Äôs actually something you can get on your latte at Collectivo. 

The Collectivo in Lincoln park right now is doubling as a Christmas tree broker, so you can sit between pine fur and smell of Christmas as you consume your peppermint fluff latte. If that‚Äôs not the peak of holiday cheer, you can slap me on the kneecaps and tell me Santa isn‚Äôt real (Santa is real, kids, *wink*). 

I‚Äôve been forced to try coffees other than Starbucks because my Starbucks app no longer works due to the fact that I refuse to update my iPhone‚Äòs iOS.  And I refuse to get Starbucks unless I‚Äôm earning double the points from my preloaded Starbucks card and ordering ahead. I also refuse to update my phone, as I buy into the conspiracy that updating a phone makes it die faster (this was an idea probably formed by a clan of people who wear tin hats and eat the same thing for breakfast, lunch and dinner everyday but I don‚Äôt care). For some reason I can‚Äôt get myself to order Starbucks at the counter when I know I have and ungodly power to summon whatever drink I can Frankenstein up (or their basic holiday menu) from anywhere using my Starbucks app on my phone. It‚Äôs that type of power that I live for. 

Maybe it‚Äôs for the best that my, because instead of getting a pumpkin cream cold foam from starbuckaroo (fake name for copyright purposes), I tried the peppermint fluff latte.

Decorating a beautiful Bouche de Noel this holiday season is an excellent project for the whole family!

We provide a frosted Yule Log cake and all the supplies to decorate it. Our moist chocolate sponge cake is rolled with vanilla Italian meringue buttercream and covered with chocolate French buttercream. The included supplies will give you everything you need to make various edible decorations like mushrooms, pine cones, field mice, and ladybugs. A link to an instructional video that will guide you in making your decorations is also provided!

Kit includes frosted cake that serves 8-12, four colors of marzipan, and other edibles to help create your masterpiece.

A limited quantity is available. Preorder only. Order online, by phone, or in person.
